  </p>

  <h2>9. Termination</h2>
  <p>
    We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service at our sole discretion, without notice, for
    conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users or the Service.
  </p>
  <p>
    You may terminate your account at any time. Upon termination, your right to use the Service
    ceases immediately, and we will delete your data in accordance with our
    <a href={~p"/privacy"}>Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
  <p>
    The Service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express
